  "deliverables": [
    "Published GitHub Releases remain the highest release-version authority",
    "Newest semantic-version Git tag becomes the console version when no GitHub Release is published",
    "Untagged pushes refresh commit and repository activity without inventing a release version",
    "GitHub synchronization messages identify release, tag, or activity-only states",
    "Hourly GitHub polling schedule repairs itself when WordPress cron state is missing",
    "GitHub Connection screen includes the Release Console repository and support link controls",
    "Mapped repository table includes a direct Sync now action for each product",
    "Public repositories can be tested without requiring a GitHub token",
    "Encrypted WordPress token storage and wp-config.php/environment overrides remain preserved",
    "All active WordPress plugin mappings, canonical identities, legacy shortcodes, accessibility, and plugin folder remain preserved",
    "Complete inherited validation and checksum-verified release packaging"
